EmailTemplate.subject: St Andrew's Cathedral School: Thank you for visiting us at Expo!
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Dear {!Lead.FirstName}
Thank you for visiting St Andrew's Cathedral School at the Schools Expo recently. I hope you found the Expo insightful and were able to have all of your questions answered.
I would like to invite you to our upcoming Head of School Tour on Tuesday 10 April at 9.00am. It's a great way to visit, meet our staff and current students and discover what makes our city school so unique.
If you are able to come along to on the tour, please let us know by replying to this email.
In the meantime, you can find out whats happening here at our St Andrews community by visiting our website, facebook page and our official youtube channel. Theyre updated daily during term time with news, photos, events and mini videos.
I look forward to welcoming you and your family to St Andrew's Cathedral School.
Regards
Bruce Perry Registrar
